article_title: Man Detained in Connection With Paris Attacks
article_text:
PARIS—French police Tuesday detained a 29-year-old man as part of the investigation into the attacks that killed 130 people in the French capital last month, a spokeswoman for the Paris prosecutors’ office said.

It wasn’t clear what role the man is alleged to have played. ​
